source.name: ENERGY STAR Certified Roof Products
source.description: Certified models meet all ENERGY STAR requirements as listed in the Version 2.3 ENERGY STAR Program Requirements for Roof Products that are effective as of July 1, 2012. A detailed listing of key efficiency criteria are available at http://www.energystar.gov/index.cfm?c=roof_prods.pr_crit_roof_products
